{"id":11130,"type":6,"name":"Fairly Legal Season 1","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/14/fa/11130_E9IeZ.jpg","rating":{"total":1,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":0,"7":0,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":5},"summary":"　　该剧讲述顶级诉讼律师Kate Reed（Sarah Shahi）在工作中长期目睹官僚主义和不公正的判决结果，对律师这个职业产生了强烈反感。她决定改行当法律调解人，专门与律师为敌（当事双方如果同意调解，就没有官司，没有官司就不需要律师）。 \r\n　　Kate利用自己丰富的法律知识和女性特有的直觉，再加上天不怕地不怕的性格，成功介入了许多惹人瞩目的矛盾冲突－－既有世界500强企业的大官司，也有因感情问题而闹离婚的小案子。 \r\n　　父亲去世后，Kate一直与继母（Virginia Williams）不合，可继母偏偏是她的老板……与此同时，她与在地区检察官办公室当律师的前夫（Michael Trucco）依然藕断丝连－－当不成夫妻不要紧，至少还可以当「床伴」。还好Kate身边有一位好助手（Baron Vaughn），这位文雅的「书生」总是替她把一切都打点好，让她可以安安心心过完每一天。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>律政佳人 第一季</li><li><span>配角: </span><a href=\"/person/24140\">Dean Norris</a></li><li><span>集数: </span>10</li><li><span>开始: </span>January 20, 2011</li><li><span>类型: </span>律政</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>频道: </span>USA Network</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt1586676</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":2,"dropped":2},"tags":[{"name":"剧情","count":1},{"name":"美剧","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":65966,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/65966","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":65967,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/65967","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":65968,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/65968","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":65969,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/65969","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":65970,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/65970","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":65971,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/65971","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":65972,"url":"http: